    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You make a melee attack with your held weapon, which deals an additional 3d6 damage. If hit, the target must make a save to avoid being knocked back 15 ft. If the target impacts a solid object, both it and the object suffer 1d6 damage for every 15 ft of the knockback effect, and the target falls @Condition[prone]{prone}.<br><br>Once used, your weapon flies from your grip and lands in the target's square. A Strength check (DC 20) lets it land in a square adjacent to you instead, and if you beat the DC by 5 or more you don't lose your grip on the weapon at all.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 2 Chakra to increase the additional damage by 1d6 and the knockback by 5 ft, up to 10d6 and 50 ft total.</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> Each step grants you a +2 bonus to Strength checks made to maintain your grip on the weapon.</p>\n",
